{"tid":2158228,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許智峯反駁大公報踐踏新聞自由指控","createTime":"2020-08-15T14:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T05:59:25.000Z","uid":313615,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6fec0e2b8a575b6e2ed289ad8e2cc91d5090ab5","tid":2158228,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"民主黨議員許智峯被神秘車輛跟蹤，對質期間輕微撞到許，車上兩人其後獲警放行。《大公報》發聲明，形容當時許與幾名身份不明人士「粗言辱罵，咆哮着大力拍打車身，並欲強行打開車門，拉記者下車」。許智峯譴責《大公》指控失實，表明過程中從無侮罵或拖司機出車。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯在聲明中，要求《大公報》立即撤回聲明及道歉，並將循法律途徑追究。<br />\n<br />\n許並向傳媒提供了一段影片，顯示13日及14日車上攝影機所拍到該車輛跟蹤片段以及許智峯當晚要求對質時所拍下的片段。許智峯又在聲明重申，車上二人沒有展示過記者證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1294642232734048257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1294642232734048257&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELw0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=300a49c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1294642232734048257&h=aae341b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1294642232734048257</a>"},{"pid":"311b8b81292f429c3586f77bbe4c9f4a0bfaec52","tid":2158228,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178843345631203/posts/1581814565334067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178843345631203%2Fposts%2F1581814565334067%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELw0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=1e5ce4b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178843345631203/posts/1581814565334067/</a>"},{"pid":"7da8f82655586b6029672291b2a1920575078fe1","tid":2158228,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5400808105b35b675b3c1adb80303a18e667952d","tid":2158228,"uid":296369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"